animeTitle: Norman the Snowman: Kita no Kuni no Aurora
animeDescription: As the first snow falls on a town in the northern country, a boy sneaks out of his house to board a northbound train with his friend “Norman the Snowman.” They are off to witness the beautiful wonders of nature that Norman had always talked about.(Source: JFF Plus)
